### 5. Retry Safety

All consumers now **re-throw errors** instead of silently swallowing them. This allows the existing Kafka retry loop (in `kafka.js`) and DLQ routing to function correctly:

```
Consumer throws → Kafka retries (up to maxRetries) → DLQ topic
```

